  <brief_title>Pharmacokinetic Drug Interaction Study Following Co-administration of Valsartan, Hydrochlorothiazide and Amlodipine in Patients With Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Multiple Dose, Open-label, Four-cohort, Parallel Study to Assess the Pharmacokinetic Drug Interaction Following Co-administration of Valsartan, Hydrochlorothiazide and Amlodipine in Patients With Hypertension.</official_title>
