  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine potential pharmacokinetic drug-drug interaction
      when three drugs (valsartan, amlodipine, and hydrochlorothiazide) are co-administered.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
